<br>
New skald here ... recently respecced at level 20 from axe to hammer. I wanted to have an advantage in doing more damage against certain classes/armor so I thought crushing damage would be better. So far I have been kind of down about the slooowwwness of hammers. I'll be tanking something and think to myself, &quot;I haven't swung yet... still haven't swung....am I going LD.... am I having terrible lag ... still haven't swung yet... ah there it is.&quot; So my question is.. is there any way to improve the swing speed of hammers? I'm a norse, added 10 to con, str, and char at creation, currently at 23BS, 17H, and 4P, and am using the Njessi 2-handed hammer. <br>
