reenFromWeb?topicID=394.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> swing speed</span><hr size=1> The following inrease swing speed.<br>
<br>
QUI (50-250, per 10 points = 1% faster swing..and 1% more base damage as a result). 250-300 = 1% per 20 points.<br>
<br>
Healer haste buff, and celerity: Can be up to 20% from a full aug healer (gimp..hope you never see one), and celerity is around 30% usually..so you can be hitting substantial faster and for more damage with a healer w/aug.<br>
<br>
Mastery of Arms Realm ability (too expensive, unless you are R8, I wouldnt even consider it).<br>
<br>
Haste procs (with alchemy I hear)<br>
<br>
And...as you know..faster hammers.  Although, 1H hammers do less damage per DPS than their 2H counterparts.  Recall 2H weapons give a bonus to damage...around 20% all the way up to around 40% at 50 spec (modified even <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   That's above and beyond the DPS listed.<br>
<br>
